creator: Various
description:
This is a collection of 19 poems read by LibriVox volunteers for August 2013.
Contributors: David Wales; Gman; Kasper Nijsen; Larry Wilson; Laurie Anne Walden; Leonard Wilson; Winston Tharp

This project contains the following:

Promise by Paul Laurence Dunbar (1872-1906) The Seedling by Paul Laurence Dunbar (1872-1906) Fulfilment by Paul Laurence Dunbar (1872-1906) California City Landscape by Carl Sandburg (1878-1967) A Christmas Legend by Caroline Atwater Mason (1853-1939) Easter Angels by Phillips Brooks (1835-1893) An Easter Carol by Phillips Brooks (1835-1893) The Easter Flower by Phillips Brooks (1835-1893) They All Want to Play Hamlet by Carl Sandburg (1878-1967) The Mountain Whippoorwill by Stephen Vincent Benét (1898-1943) Music I Heard by Conrad Aiken (1889-1973) Not to Keep by Robert Frost (1874-1963) On My First Son by Ben Jonson (1572-1637) Outcast by Caroline Atwater Mason (1853-1939) The Road Not Taken by Robert Frost (1874-1963) To Marguerite by Matthew Arnold (1822-1888) Under a Picture of the Magdalene by Caroline Atwater Mason (1853-1939) The Unknown Beloved by John Hall Wheelock (1886-1978) Windflower Leaf by Carl Sandburg (1878-1967)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
